1. On je našao svoje sreće u prošlosti*. (He found his happiness in the past.)
2. Prošlosti* su nas obeležile i sada se trudimo da promenimo budućnost. (The past has marked us and now we are trying to change the future.)
3. Ne možemo mijenjati prošlost*, ali možemo učiniti da budućnost bude bolja. (We cannot change the past, but we can make the future better.)
4. Svi smo učili iz grešaka prošlosti*. (We all learned from the mistakes of the past.)
5. Prošlosti* nikada ne treba zaboraviti. (The past should never be forgotten.)